WASHINGTON, DC—

Tun lokacin da cutar ebola ta bullo kai a Najeriya gwamnatin jihar Filato ta dukufa wajen wayar wa alʼummarta kai dangane da cutar.

Ta wayar dasu akan yadda ake kamuwa da cutar da kuma abun da zasu yi su kauce kamuwa da ita.
Kwamishanan kiwon lafiya na jihar Dr Pam Dakwar yace maʼaikatarsa ta horas da maʼaikata wajen dari uku domin shirin ko ta kwana wadanda zasu taimaka wajen bada bayanai da kulawa da wadanda watakila zasu kamu da cutar.

Gwamnatin jihar ta bada nera miliyan casaʼin da biyar domin sayen kayan aiki da tanada wuraren da zaʼa kula da mutane.

Shugaban karamar hukumar Mangu yace zasu bada goyon baya da hadin kan malaman addini da sarakunan gargajiya wajen wayarwa jamaʼa kai akan illar cutar

Ga rahoton Zainab Babaji.
Gwamnatin Jihar Filato ta Dauki Matakan Kare Jamaʼarta Daga Kamuwa da Cutar Ebola - 3'00" Kwandon Shirye-shirye na Sauko Da Sauti

